window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Winter has come, but Dar won’t be able to rest just yet. An emissary of The White comes through Hearthway headed toward Bellhaven to investigate rumors of their treatment toward the ancient races.</p> <p>While entirely true, Dar has already taken care of those responsible and follows Karn into Bellhaven to observe and further his own goals.</p> <p>For when the little dao tree absorbed the Mo in the form of a colossal spider, it changed and sprung up new potential within him. Dar wants to see if the devil problem in Bellhaven can’t lead him to another Mo and more power.</p> <p>Yet the trip to Bellhaven yielded more information than he expected. The winter was just the first of their problems.</p>"; 
